msg: Added the optional.jar from the ant distribution. Since it
probably makes sense to have the ant.jar and the optional.jar
to be from the same (nighly) snapshot and there is no way
I could find out from which snapshot the old jar was I replaced
the ant.jar with the jar from the same snapshot as the optional.jar.
